{"tid":1727412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地同藍絲黑警有咩分別？","createTime":"2019-11-16T12:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:20:24.000Z","uid":141038,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64cbd3e3313796989af14ba6e7d84cd0172075a5","tid":1727412,"uid":141038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"唔係割，而係想反思我地既行為，當市民清路障，真係有必要要打嗎？<br />\n<br />\n佢地清，我地咪再放返，去到打佢地依步，我地同濫用暴力既黑警、藍絲，有分別嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民心的確唔係我地首要顧及，但的確係有一啲更好既做法，能令我地更團結，更多人加入。<br />\n各位手足，保持初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cb3cdefe3da5bf7b0c68293a8b7b054fe641f3","tid":1727412,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2F